headline: S&P 500 Gains & Losses Today: HP, Best Buy Stocks Drop as Tariffs Weigh On Outlook
summary: The S&P 500 added 0.4% on Thursday, May 29, 2025, after the latest earnings report from AI chip giant Nvidia and a court ruling against some of Trump's tariff policies.
